<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>영원의 순간 — A Moment That Lasts Forever</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css?v=20260530e">
</head>
<body>


<!-- ── 운영자 로그인 ── -->
<div id="screen-login" class="screen active">
  <div style="min-height:100vh; background:linear-gradient(rgba(248,245,240,0.58), rgba(248,245,240,0.58)), url('media/operator-login-bg-poster.jpg') center/cover no-repeat; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:24px;">
    <div style="width:100%; max-width:360px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9); backdrop-filter:blur(10px); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.75); border-radius:20px; padding:36px 28px; box-shadow:0 12px 32px rgba(44,31,26,0.10);">
      <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:26px;">
        <div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:30px; color:var(--deep-rose); margin-bottom:6px;"><span style="font-style:italic;">A Moment</span> That Lasts</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.7;">운영자 로그인 후<br>웨딩 사이트 생성 및 관리를 진행하세요</div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom:12px;">
        <div style="font-size:11px; color:var(--text-muted); margin-bottom:6px;">아이디</div>
        <input type="text" id="login-username" class="form-input" placeholder="아이디 입력" autocomplete="username" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom:12px;">
        <div style="font-size:11px; color:var(--text-muted); margin-bottom:6px;">비밀번호</div>
        <input type="password" id="login-password" class="form-input" placeholder="비밀번호 입력" autocomplete="current-password" onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter') handleOperatorLogin()" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      </div>

      <div id="login-error" style="min-height:18px; margin-bottom:12px; font-size:12px; color:var(--rose); text-align:center;"></div>

      <button id="login-btn" class="btn-primary" onclick="handleOperatorLogin()">로그인</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- ── 운영자 홈 (대시보드) ── -->
<div id="screen-operator" class="screen">
  <div class="admin-layout">
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="brand-title">A Moment<br>That Lasts</div>
        <div class="brand-subtitle">SERVICE ADMIN CONSOLE</div>
      </div>

      <div class="nav-section-label">MAIN</div>
      <button class="nav-item active">📊 대시보드</button>
      <button class="nav-item" onclick="opGoCreate()">✨ 사이트 생성</button>
      <button class="nav-item" onclick="opGoManage()">📋 사이트 관리</button>
      <button class="nav-item" onclick="opGoAdmin()">📸 업로드 관리</button>

      <div class="nav-section-label">SYSTEM</div>
      <button class="nav-item">🧾 운영 로그</button>

      <div class="sidebar-footer">
        <strong>운영자 전용 화면</strong>
        <p>신랑·신부 또는 하객에게 노출되지 않는 서비스 배포/관리 콘솔입니다.</p>
        <button onclick="operatorLogout()" style="width:100%;margin-top:12px;padding:9px;border:1px solid rgba(139,74,56,.15);border-radius:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.5);color:var(--deep-rose);font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:background .2s">로그아웃</button>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <main class="main">
      <header class="topbar">
        <div>
          <div class="breadcrumb">Admin Console / Dashboard</div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- ── 시스템 상태 스크롤 티커 ── -->
      <div class="status-ticker-wrap">
        <div class="status-ticker-track">
          <div class="status-ticker-inner" id="status-ticker-inner">
            <span class="ticker-item">🟡 Spring Boot API — <span id="op-system-api">CHECKING</span></span>
            <span class="ticker-sep">◆</span>
            <span class="ticker-item">🟡 MySQL Database — <span id="op-system-db">CHECKING</span></span>
            <span class="ticker-sep">◆</span>
            <span class="ticker-item">🟢 QR Generator — ACTIVE</span>
            <span class="ticker-sep">◆</span>
            <span class="ticker-item">🟡 Upload Directory — <span id="op-system-dashboard">CHECKING</span></span>
            <span class="ticker-sep">◆</span>
            <span class="ticker-item ticker-summary-item" id="ticker-summary">총 사이트 <span class="ts-sites" id="op-stat-total-sites-t">-</span>건 · 사진 <span class="ts-photos" id="op-stat-total-photos-t">-</span>장 · 하객 <span class="ts-guests" id="op-stat-total-guests-t">-</span>명</span>
            <span class="ticker-sep">◆</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-label">전체 생성 사이트</div>
          <div class="stat-value"><span id="op-stat-total-sites">-</span></div>
          <div class="stat-caption">누적 이벤트 수</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-label">진행 예정 행사</div>
          <div class="stat-value"><span id="op-stat-future-sites">-</span></div>
          <div class="stat-caption">QR 활성 대기</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-label">누적 업로드 사진</div>
          <div class="stat-value"><span id="op-stat-total-photos">-</span></div>
          <div class="stat-caption">전체 이벤트 합산</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-label">참여 하객 수</div>
          <div class="stat-value"><span id="op-stat-total-guests">-</span></div>
          <div class="stat-caption">게시물 작성 기준</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ── 월별 결혼식 서비스 현황 차트 ── -->
      <section class="monthly-chart-section">
        <div class="monthly-chart-header">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow" style="font-size:11px; margin-bottom:10px;">MONTHLY ANALYTICS</div>
            <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:22px; font-weight:400; color:var(--deep-rose); margin-bottom:6px;">월별 결혼식 서비스 현황</h3>
            <p style="font-size:13px; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.6;">생성된 결혼식 사이트의 월별 추이를 확인합니다</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="monthly-chart-body" id="chart-body">
          <div class="chart-placeholder">데이터 로딩 중...</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ── 운영 메모 TODO ── -->
      <section class="todo-section">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:14px;">
          <div>
            <div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:400;color:var(--deep-rose);">운영 메모</div>
            <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:2px;">체크하면 완료, 엔터로 추가</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="todo-wrap" id="todo-list">
          <div class="todo-item">
            <div class="todo-cb" onclick="toggleTodo(this)"></div>
            <span class="todo-text">오늘 결혼식 2건 QR 상태 확인</span>
          </div>
          <div class="todo-item">
            <div class="todo-cb" onclick="toggleTodo(this)"></div>
            <span class="todo-text">신규 업로드 게시물 관리자 검토</span>
          </div>
          <div class="todo-item">
            <div class="todo-cb" onclick="toggleTodo(this)"></div>
            <span class="todo-text">QR 만료 예정 행사 7일前 알림</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="todo-input-row">
          <input type="text" id="todo-input" placeholder="메모 추가 (예: QR 테스트 필요)" onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter') addTodo()">
          <button class="todo-add-btn" onclick="addTodo()">추가</button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section-grid" style="grid-template-columns:1fr;">
        <div class="panel">
          <div class="panel-head">
            <div>
              <h2>최근 생성된 사이트</h2>
              <p>운영자가 관리 중인 웨딩 이벤트 목록입니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <table class="event-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>이벤트</th>
                <th>날짜</th>
                <th>사진</th>
                <th>상태</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody id="op-recent-events-body">
              <tr><td colspan="4" style="color:var(--muted);padding:18px 0;">불러오는 중...</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── 사이트 관리 화면 ── -->
<div id="screen-manage" class="screen">
  <div style="min-height:100vh; background:#F8F5F0; display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
    <div class="console-topbar">
      <div class="console-topbar-left">
        <button class="back-btn" onclick="showScreen('operator')">← 홈</button>
      </div>
      <div class="console-topbar-center">
        <div class="console-topbar-title">A Moment That Lasts</div>
        <div class="console-topbar-label">사이트 관리</div>
      </div>
      <div class="console-topbar-right">
        <span class="console-topbar-badge" id="manage-total" style="margin-right:8px;">총 0건</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="flex:1; padding:32px 40px; overflow-y:auto; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:24px;">
      <section class="manage-toolbar-card" style="margin-top:0;">
        <div class="manage-search-wrap">
          <label class="toolbar-label" for="manage-search">검색</label>
          <input id="manage-search" class="manage-search-input" type="text" placeholder="커플명, 행사코드, 날짜로 찾기" oninput="setManageSearchKeyword(this.value)">
        </div>
        <div class="manage-sort-wrap">
          <label class="toolbar-label" for="manage-sort">정렬</label>
          <select id="manage-sort" class="manage-sort-select" onchange="setManageSort(this.value)">
            <option value="weddingDateDesc">예식일 최신순</option>
            <option value="weddingDateAsc">예식일 오래된순</option>
            <option value="createdAtDesc">생성일 최신순</option>
            <option value="photoCountDesc">사진 많은순</option>
            <option value="guestCountDesc">하객 많은순</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="manage-filter-wrap">
          <button id="manage-filter-all" class="manage-filter-btn active" onclick="setManageStatusFilter('all')">전체</button>
          <button id="manage-filter-today" class="manage-filter-btn" onclick="setManageStatusFilter('today')">오늘</button>
          <button id="manage-filter-future" class="manage-filter-btn" onclick="setManageStatusFilter('future')">예정</button>
          <button id="manage-filter-past" class="manage-filter-btn" onclick="setManageStatusFilter('past')">지난 행사</button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="manage-today-section" class="manage-section-card featured" style="padding:24px 26px;">
        <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; margin-bottom:16px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <div style="width:10px; height:10px; border-radius:50%; background:#4CAF50; animation:pulse2 1.5s infinite;"></div>
          <div class="manage-section-label-text" style="color:#2E7D32;">오늘의 결혼식</div>
          <div id="today-count" class="manage-count-chip">0건</div>
        </div>
        <div id="today-list" class="manage-today-grid"></div>
      </section>

      <section id="manage-future-section" class="manage-section-card" style="padding:24px 26px;">
        <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; margin-bottom:16px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <div style="width:10px; height:10px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--gold);"></div>
          <div class="manage-section-label-text" style="color:var(--dark-gold);">예정된 결혼식</div>
          <div id="future-count" class="manage-count-chip">0건</div>
        </div>
        <div id="future-list" class="manage-list-stack"></div>
      </section>

      <section id="manage-past-section" class="manage-section-card muted" style="padding:24px 26px;">
        <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:10px; margin-bottom:16px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <div style="width:10px; height:10px; border-radius:50%; background:#9E9E9E;"></div>
            <div class="manage-section-label-text" style="color:var(--text-muted);">지난 결혼식</div>
            <div id="past-count" class="manage-count-chip">0건</div>
          </div>
          <button id="manage-past-toggle" class="panel-link-btn" onclick="togglePastSection()">펼치기</button>
        </div>
        <div id="past-list-wrap" class="manage-collapsible-wrap">
          <div id="past-list" class="manage-list-stack"></div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
@keyframes pulse2 { 0%,100%{opacity:1;} 50%{opacity:0.3;} }
</style>

<!-- ── QR 발급 화면 ── -->
<div id="screen-qr" class="screen">
  <div class="console-shell qr-shell">
    <header class="console-header compact">
      <div class="console-header-main">
        <button class="console-back-btn" onclick="showScreen('operator')">← 홈</button>
        <div>
          <div class="console-eyebrow">SITE CREATION CONSOLE</div>
          <div class="console-brand-title"><span>A Moment</span> Launch Studio</div>
          <div class="console-brand-subtitle">한 번의 입력으로 웨딩 사이트와 QR 입장 흐름을 함께 준비합니다.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="console-header-side">
        <div class="console-badge">운영자 전용</div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="qr-main-grid">
      <section class="qr-form-column">
        <article class="console-card">
          <div class="console-card-head">
            <div>
              <div class="panel-kicker">BASIC INFO</div>
              <h2>커플 및 일정 정보</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="console-form-grid two-col">
            <div>
              <label class="toolbar-label" for="qr-groom">신랑 이름</label>
              <input type="text" id="qr-groom" class="form-input" placeholder="신랑 이름 (최대 5글자)" maxlength="5" oninput="clearQR()">
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="toolbar-label" for="qr-bride">신부 이름</label>
              <input type="text" id="qr-bride" class="form-input" placeholder="신부 이름 (최대 5글자)" maxlength="5" oninput="clearQR()">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="console-form-block">
            <label class="toolbar-label" for="wedding-date">결혼식 날짜 <span class="required-dot">*</span></label>
            <input type="date" id="wedding-date" class="form-input" oninput="clearQR(); validateDate(this); updateValidityRange()">
          </div>
          <div class="console-form-block validity-block">
            <div class="toolbar-label">QR 유효 기간 <span class="toolbar-label-note">결혼식 날짜 기준 최대 ±5일</span></div>
            <div class="console-form-grid two-col validity-grid">
              <div>
                <label class="micro-label" for="qr-start">시작일</label>
                <input type="date" id="qr-start" class="form-input" oninput="validateValidityRange()">
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="micro-label" for="qr-end">종료일</label>
                <input type="date" id="qr-end" class="form-input" oninput="validateValidityRange()">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="validity-msg" class="console-helper-text">결혼식 날짜를 먼저 선택해 주세요</div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="console-card">
          <div class="console-card-head">
            <div>
              <div class="panel-kicker">INVITATION</div>
              <h2>청첩장 업로드</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 타입 토글 -->
          <div style="display:flex; background:var(--cream); border-radius:10px; padding:3px; margin-bottom:16px;">
            <button id="inv-type-img" onclick="setInvitationType('image')"
              style="flex:1; padding:8px; border:none; border-radius:8px; background:var(--white); color:var(--deep-rose); font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif; font-size:12px; cursor:pointer; box-shadow:0 1px 3px var(--shadow); transition:all 0.2s; font-weight:500;">
              🖼 이미지 업로드
            </button>
            <button id="inv-type-url" onclick="setInvitationType('url')"
              style="flex:1; padding:8px; border:none; border-radius:8px; background:transparent; color:var(--text-muted); font-family:'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif; font-size:12px; cursor:pointer; transition:all 0.2s;">
              🔗 링크 삽입
            </button>
          </div>
          <!-- 이미지 업로드 영역 -->
          <div id="inv-image-section">
            <div id="invitation-drop" onclick="document.getElementById('invitation-input').click()"
              style="border:1.5px dashed var(--blush); border-radius:12px; padding:32px 20px; text-align:center; cursor:pointer; transition:border-color 0.2s; background:var(--cream);"
              onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='var(--rose)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='var(--blush)'">
              <div style="font-size:28px; margin-bottom:8px; opacity:0.5;">💌</div>
              <div style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-muted);">클릭하여 청첩장 이미지 업로드</div>
              <div style="font-size:11px; color:var(--text-muted); margin-top:4px;">JPG, PNG · 최대 10MB</div>
              <input type="file" id="invitation-input" accept="image/*" style="display:none" onchange="previewInvitation(event)">
            </div>
            <div id="invitation-preview" style="display:none; margin-top:12px; text-align:center;">
              <img id="invitation-img" style="max-width:100%; max-height:200px; border-radius:8px; border:1px solid var(--border); object-fit:contain;">
              <button onclick="clearInvitation()" style="display:block; margin:8px auto 0; font-size:11px; color:var(--rose); border:none; background:transparent; cursor:pointer;">✕ 제거</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 링크 입력 영역 -->
          <div id="inv-url-section" style="display:none;">
            <input type="url" id="invitation-url-input" class="form-input"
              placeholder="https://toourguest.com/cards/..."
              oninput="previewInvitationUrl(this.value)" style="margin-bottom:8px;">
            <div id="inv-url-preview" style="display:none; border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:10px; overflow:hidden; background:var(--cream);">
              <div style="padding:8px 12px; font-size:11px; color:var(--text-muted); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px;">
                <span>🔗</span> <span id="inv-url-label" style="overflow:hidden; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;"></span>
                <button onclick="clearInvitationUrl()" style="margin-left:auto; border:none; background:transparent; color:var(--rose); cursor:pointer; font-size:11px; flex-shrink:0;">✕ 제거</button>
              </div>
              <iframe id="inv-url-iframe" style="width:100%; height:200px; border:none; pointer-events:none;"></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- ── FAQ 설정 ── -->
        <article class="console-card">
          <div class="console-card-head with-meta">
            <div>
              <div class="panel-kicker">FAQ</div>
              <h2>자주 묻는 질문</h2>
            </div>
            <button onclick="addFaqItem()" class="faq-add-btn">＋ 질문 추가</button>
          </div>
          <div id="faq-edit-list"></div>
          <div id="faq-edit-empty" style="text-align:center; padding:28px 0; color:var(--text-muted); font-size:13px;">
            💬 하객이 자주 궁금해할 질문을 추가해 주세요<br>
            <span style="font-size:11px; margin-top:6px; display:block; line-height:1.6; color:var(--text-muted);">
              주차 안내 · 복장 규정 · 식사 정보 · 위치 안내 등
            </span>
          </div>
        </article>

      </section>

      <section class="qr-side-column">
        <article class="console-card">
          <div class="console-card-head with-meta">
            <div>
              <div class="panel-kicker">GALLERY ASSETS</div>
              <h2>웨딩 사진 컬렉션</h2>
            </div>
            <div id="wedding-photo-count" class="console-summary-chip">0 / 3~8장</div>
          </div>
